1LT Scarbrough;

These are my current expectations.

Note that, allegedly, there are two "Elrods" in 3 / 3. I only have personal
biographical information on one. Query MAJ Crosby / 1LT Riley for more
information if they even have it.

We will obviously have to adjust, but this is my current estimate.

1LT Overton;

Obviously, this was edited from the Planning Portal format. Incorporate
this information into the Planning Portal, but make sure that the format in
the portal remains the same.

I do not know the names or definitively how many attachments that we will
be receiving. I will refine. I monitor PAX flow on the 3 RGT TPFDD - Ops
Synch TNMAN-26 (29 APR 26) document, which I will forward to y'all later
today.

Should either of you have any questions, please let me know.
